channel.title: How do i make a silabsoft server?
channel.description: i have been searching for days and haven't found good results, i need to know EVERYTHING i need and where i can get it, i need a good server to download, a good walkthrough on how to make a server, and codes for ::master and ::jail and ::money and stuff like that, i also have my server ip made, fr3akazoidscape.no-ip.info but i don't know how to log it in, i need to know EVERYTHING!!!

item.title: How do i make a silabsoft server?
item.dc:creator: @wrath0fgufix wrath0fgufix
item.description:
@wrath0fgufix wrote:

ok you can look at stormcuttersguide but i will give you a brief summary.

Ok download win rar and the newest java then find a source and dl it onto win rar as of "figmentsafter that you need to change some sort or variable settings that part i do not remember then go to your compute click on the firewall settings which is the brick wall with the earth behind it go to a place where you see “add port” you may have to change tabs while there then fill the first thing with “server” next fill it with a port.

Then you’ll see two dots filler thingy do the one on the right. Also you might want to extract your files to the desktop. this is as far as i can get to.

Feel free to give rep++!
